Pac-Man 10 Requirements
Mandatory:

The game Must increase the players score when a pellet is consumed.

The game Must display the users score, remaining lives, and current level.

The game Must decrease the players life count when a player allides with a ghost.

The game Must stop pac-man from running through walls.

The game Must increase in difficulty as levels progress.

The game Must end when the player has 0 lives.

The game Must advance to the next level when all pellets have been consumed.

The game Must allow pacman to consume ghost during the frightened state.

The system must have 4 ghost enemies.

The system must populate the map with pellets.
